                        <interp inst="t18550226-name-381" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN CHILD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a plumber. I laid on the pipe to No. 30, St. Mary-street—there were three joints; this pipe has only one, but it is one of my joints.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I found it.</p>
